N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 360-9.2 - Demonstration applications

State Regulations
A social services district may apply to participate in
the CHCEP by submitting a proposal which describes how the program would be
implemented in the district if the department approved the proposal. All
proposals must be submitted by February 28, 1989, or such later date specified
by the department. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18

360-9.2
